{"name": "odoo-addon-account-invoice-discount-display-amount", "metadata": {"name": "odoo-addon-account-invoice-discount-display-amount", "version": "16.0.1.1.1", "classifiers": ["Framework :: Odoo", "Framework :: Odoo :: 16.0", "License :: OSI Approved :: GNU Affero General Public License v3", "Programming Language :: Python"], "home_page": "https://github.com/OCA/account-invoicing", "license": "AGPL-3", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["odoo"], "summary": "Show total discount applied and total without discount on invoices.", "upload_time": 1726658111}, "documentation": ["---\nsubstitutions:\n  badge1: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/maturity-Beta-yellow.png\n    :alt: Beta\n    :target: https://odoo-community.org/page/development-status\n    ```\n  badge2: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/licence-AGPL--3-blue.png\n    :alt: 'License: AGPL-3'\n    :target: http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl-3.0-standalone.html\n    ```\n  badge3: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/github-OCA%2Faccount--invoicing-lightgray.png?logo=github\n    :alt: OCA/account-invoicing\n    :target: https://github.com/OCA/account-invoicing/tree/16.0/account_invoice_discount_display_amount\n    ```\n  badge4: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/weblate-Translate%20me-F47D42.png\n    :alt: Translate me on Weblate\n    :target: https://translation.odoo-community.org/projects/account-invoicing-16-0/account-invoicing-16-0-account_invoice_discount_display_amount\n    ```\n  badge5: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/runboat-Try%20me-875A7B.png\n    :alt: Try me on Runboat\n    :target: https://runboat.odoo-community.org/builds?repo=OCA/account-invoicing&target_branch=16.0\n    ```\n---\n\n# Account Invoice Discount Display Amount\n\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n% !! This file is generated by oca-gen-addon-readme !!\n% !! changes will be overwritten.                   !!\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n% !! source digest: sha256:f627f2f863d0d9b91467c2db59d91fbdae94661e56aa11bdc730544a7df65aa5\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n\n{{ badge1 }} {{ badge2 }} {{ badge3 }} {{ badge4 }} {{ badge5 }}\n\nThis module allows to show the total discount amount\napplied to an invoice, both in the backend and the\ninvoice PDF repot.\n\n**Table of contents**\n\n```{contents}\n:local: true\n```\n\n## Configuration\n\nTo configure this module, you need to:\n\n1. No configuration instructions needed.\n\n## Usage\n\nTo use this module, you need to:\n\n1. Apply a discount on an invoice line.\n2. The values 'Discount Total' and 'Total Without Discount'\n   will be automatically updated.\n\n## Bug Tracker\n\nBugs are tracked on [GitHub Issues](https://github.com/OCA/account-invoicing/issues).\nIn case of trouble, please check there if your issue has already been reported.\nIf you spotted it first, help us to smash it by providing a detailed and welcomed\n[feedback](https://github.com/OCA/account-invoicing/issues/new?body=module:%20account_invoice_discount_display_amount%0Aversion:%2016.0%0A%0A**Steps%20to%20reproduce**%0A-%20...%0A%0A**Current%20behavior**%0A%0A**Expected%20behavior**).\n\nDo not contact contributors directly about support or help with technical issues.\n\n## Credits\n\n### Authors\n\n- Sygel\n\n### Contributors\n\n- Manuel Regidor \\<<mailto:manuel.regidor@sygel.es>>\n- Alexei Rivera \\<<mailto:arivera@archeti.com>>\n- \\[APSL-Nagarro\\](<https://apsl.tech>):\n  \\* Santi Amor\u00f3s \\<<mailto:samoros@apsl.net>>\n\n### Maintainers\n\nThis module is maintained by the OCA.\n\n```{image} https://odoo-community.org/logo.png\n:alt: Odoo Community Association\n:target: https://odoo-community.org\n```\n\nOCA, or the Odoo Community Association, is a nonprofit organization whose\nmission is to support the collaborative development of Odoo features and\npromote its widespread use.\n\nThis module is part of the [OCA/account-invoicing](https://github.com/OCA/account-invoicing/tree/16.0/account_invoice_discount_display_amount) project on GitHub.\n\nYou are welcome to contribute. To learn how please visit <https://odoo-community.org/page/Contribute>.\n"], "modules": [{"name": "odoo.addons.account_invoice_discount_display_amount.models", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "odoo.addons.account_invoice_discount_display_amount.models.account_move", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.account_invoice_discount_display_amount.models..account_move", "project": null}}, {"name": "odoo.addons.account_invoice_discount_display_amount.models.account_move_line", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.account_invoice_discount_display_amount.models..account_move_line", "project": null}}]}, {"name": "odoo.addons.account_invoice_discount_display_amount.models.account_move", "documentation": ["Copyright 2022 Manuel Regidor <manuel.regidor@sygel.es>", "License AGPL-3.0 or later (http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl)."], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [{"name": "odoo.addons.account_invoice_discount_display_amount.models.account_move.AccountMove", "bases": ["models.Model"], "methods": [{"name": "odoo.addons.account_invoice_discount_display_amount.models.account_move.AccountMove._compute_discount_total", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}], "class_variables": [{"name": "odoo.addons.account_invoice_discount_display_amount.models.account_move.AccountMove._inherit", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.account_invoice_discount_display_amount.models.account_move.AccountMove.discount_total", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.account_invoice_discount_display_amount.models.account_move.AccountMove.price_total_no_discount", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "instance_variables": [], "inner_classes": [], "documentation": []}], "exports": []